old text-gray-900 group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors line-clamp-1\">德国工业巨石的绿色心跳：从鲁尔矿场到黑森林的疗愈之旅</h4>\n                    <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-500 mt-1 line-clamp-1\">The Green Heartbeat of Germany‘s Industrial Giants: From Ruhr Mines to Black Forest Therapy</p>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              </a>\n            </div>",
